Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: •TD Tower offers 7 storeys of office space and street level retail space for a total rentable area of 82,000. •The Property is located at the southwest corner of 12th Avenue and Hamilton Street in the heart of Downtown Regina.•The tenants include TD Bank,, Gerrand Rath Johnson LLP., Emsley & Associates and Horizon Laser Vision Centre.•Centrally located in the downtown core, at the southwest corner of 12th Avenue and Hamilton Street, surrounded by mid-rise and high rise office structures ensure premium visibility  to both vehicle and pedestrian traffic.•Location benefits from proximity to high-end retail including the Cornwall Centre, Regina’s largest mall.

Main floor office/retail opportunity. The current space includes a large reception/meeting space, smaller office area, private washroom and kitchenette/breakroom. The 1,200 SF suite has a bright, clean design with ample natural light, contemporary finishes, and vinyl plank flooring. The kitchenette is well equipped with all necessary appliances including a full-size oven, refrigerator, and microwave.
